WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:21.840 --> 00:00:27.840
For it reaches to the highest mountain.

00:00:30.040 --> 00:00:34.200
Those are communion cups from the last couple times.

00:00:34.880 --> 00:00:38.430
I have to start picking up my stuff a little bit more.

00:00:39.080 --> 00:00:40.493
Oh, there it goes.

00:00:40.493 --> 00:00:41.200
All four.

00:00:41.200 --> 00:00:43.120
Bummer.

00:00:43.120 --> 00:00:46.083
Is anybody here?

00:00:46.083 --> 00:00:47.070
Yeah.

00:00:51.720 --> 00:00:54.600
Father, I plead the blood of Jesus.

00:00:55.840 --> 00:01:01.520
Thank you, Father, for your angels that watch over us tonight as we pray.

00:01:01.520 --> 00:01:06.599
Thank you, Father, that we only pray with your heart, no flesh.

00:01:06.599 --> 00:01:08.640
Thank you, Lord.

00:01:08.640 --> 00:01:15.200
We go right into the throne, Lord.

00:01:23.135 --> 00:01:26.510
Ready?

00:01:27.340 --> 00:01:29.800
Good evening, family.

00:01:29.800 --> 00:01:31.000
How are y'all doing today?

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:38.120
I just wanted to come on tonight and pray with you for a little bit.

00:01:38.440 --> 00:01:45.847
Last night when we prayed, we prayed really late to reach other parts of the world, but my heart was to pray for Australia.

00:01:46.333 --> 00:01:53.960
We prayed for Australia, Africa, and New Zealand.

00:01:54.205 --> 00:02:01.267
The Lord was showing us a great revival coming to Australia, a fresh, new, mighty outpouring of the Spirit of God.

00:02:02.120 --> 00:02:10.560
Then I was seeing new songs; new heavenly songs are going to start to come forth.

00:02:10.891 --> 00:02:14.960
The Lord was telling us to pull on that.

00:02:14.960 --> 00:02:25.540
If you are a person that makes music and writes music, I believe there's going to be heavenly music given to you as you press into the Father.

00:02:27.617 --> 00:02:34.040
You're not seeking fame or finances, but you're seeking just to worship.

00:02:34.360 --> 00:02:40.800
I believe the Lord doesn't care if we have blessings, as long as the blessings don't have us.

00:02:41.271 --> 00:02:47.120
I want you to know that's what the Lord was showing us: that there are new heavenly songs coming.

00:02:47.120 --> 00:02:53.232
There are songs that we've never heard before that are going to be glorious.

00:02:53.232 --> 00:02:58.440
Beautiful music is coming, and I would expect it right now.

00:02:59.280 --> 00:03:04.720
As we were praying last night, we saw the power grid again.

00:03:05.328 --> 00:03:23.740
As President Trump starts doing these tariffs and sanctions, the Lord showed me attacks against the power grid: Los Angeles, the Bay Area, Chicago, and New York—these places of great populations.

00:03:26.903 --> 00:03:36.907
The Lord told us last night we need to pray against power outages concerning cyber attacks and cyber warfare.

00:03:38.880 --> 00:03:54.023
I don't know who would be taking care of our power grid—maybe our army or whoever is over the cyber division—to have supernatural wisdom on how to combat the attacks that are coming.

00:03:54.560 --> 00:03:56.131
I believe they've already started.

00:03:56.446 --> 00:04:07.040
I saw Trojan horses coming in and causing disruption in our power grid in America in a greater way.

00:04:07.440 --> 00:04:20.200
It would not just be a couple of hours of power outage; we're talking a sustained amount of power being out for maybe days.

00:04:20.716 --> 00:04:25.880
I'm not trying to stir up fear; I'm trying to tell you it's something you should be prayerful about.

00:04:25.880 --> 00:04:38.140
Every single thing I bring to you is to bring prayer over our nation and for our president, for Homeland Security, the FBI, and the CIA.

00:04:38.610 --> 00:04:40.987
I just believe that there's power in prayer.

00:04:40.987 --> 00:04:50.211
Just as we saw that the man in Atlanta was going to try to do a mass shooting there and he was stopped by the authorities.

00:04:50.211 --> 00:04:51.994
All glory to God.

00:04:52.794 --> 00:05:00.260
There was confusion in the camp, and that's what we pray: that they don't have their thoughts right when they're trying to do things like that.

00:05:00.940 --> 00:05:09.130
He went in and his family told on him, and then all of a sudden the authorities said they believed that he was going back.

00:05:09.130 --> 00:05:15.840
He was scoping out the area and going back to his truck to get whatever he was going to get to hurt people.

00:05:16.400 --> 00:05:20.760
I believe this is what we're called to do.

00:05:22.063 --> 00:05:26.526
We're assembling together tonight to stop Satan's plans.

00:05:29.752 --> 00:05:32.240
Principalities work through personalities.

00:05:35.180 --> 00:05:49.480
Weak-minded people who already have a reprobate mind and are not strong in the Word are coming in, and they're trying to grab a hold of these people that already have yielded themselves over to demonic influence.

00:05:50.040 --> 00:06:00.286
We want to pray for a hedge of protection around our sporting events, including the World Series that starts tomorrow, Friday.

00:06:05.343 --> 00:06:10.020
We pray over the World Series; it's best out of seven.

00:06:18.750 --> 00:06:21.296
We are praying over our college events and any kind of major event: Thanksgiving, Black Friday, and all these things.

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:37.175
We are praying over our economy and for President Trump.

00:06:37.175 --> 00:06:44.920
As he said, he's putting more sanctions on Russia and their oil companies, so we know what will happen with that.

00:06:50.125 --> 00:06:54.057
I just believe this situation—you try to put people in a corner by touching their pocketbook—but I've seen an escalation of things.

00:06:54.057 --> 00:07:00.698
I heard one pastor say, 'Oh, Brandon, we're going to stop war altogether.

00:07:00.698 --> 00:07:03.445
' Well, that goes against Matthew 24.

00:07:03.445 --> 00:07:09.505
I'm going to line up with the Word, not with what you think.

00:07:18.780 --> 00:07:19.030
The Bible said we would have wars and rumors of wars.

00:07:19.030 --> 00:07:23.760
We'll have plagues, pestilences, and famines.

00:07:23.760 --> 00:07:28.538
This is the beginning of sorrows, and I believe we're in that timeframe.

00:07:36.446 --> 00:07:36.823
No matter how much we try to stop it, you're not going to stop the Bible.

00:07:38.700 --> 00:07:42.680
The Bible stands alone, and there is no prophetic word that's going to go against the Word of God.

00:07:42.680 --> 00:07:51.258
If it goes against the Word of God, it's not God and it's not a prophetic word; it's a false word, a false prophecy.

00:07:51.258 --> 00:07:53.635
We know what's coming, ladies and gentlemen.

00:07:53.635 --> 00:08:02.320
The Lord said to me today while I was outside, 'Brandon, there's not enough urgency.

00:08:02.320 --> 00:08:05.947
Again, you must tell My people I'm coming again.

00:08:12.516 --> 00:08:13.280
You must tell them that they need to have a sense of urgency about My coming.

00:08:13.280 --> 00:08:16.587
' I went over what I said to you all yesterday.

00:08:16.587 --> 00:08:23.560
Every time I go over everything I've said to you because I don't want any prophetic confusion.

00:08:24.544 --> 00:08:35.000
I've said a thousand times, and Paul Begley and others say, 'Brandon, you're called to be like a prophet,' but I always say I'm a watchman and I believe I have a prophetic lens.

00:08:35.000 --> 00:08:39.735
I'm able to see, and the Lord said, 'Your main focus is to bring prayer to YouTube.

00:08:39.735 --> 00:08:42.589
I want you to bring a massive prayer audience.

00:08:42.589 --> 00:08:46.420
I want a million-man and woman prayer army.

00:08:46.885 --> 00:08:51.060
As you pray, you will change things and you will protect what's coming.

00:08:51.060 --> 00:08:57.600
' If they don't know Psalm 91 and Psalm 23, they're in trouble.

00:09:12.969 --> 00:09:13.178
Is that to scare you?

00:09:13.178 --> 00:09:14.640
No, it's to prepare you.

00:09:14.640 --> 00:09:17.260
You must know the Word of God.

00:09:17.260 --> 00:09:20.560
You must understand your covenant.

00:09:27.696 --> 00:09:32.030
I know there are a lot of Word of Faith people who believe we're not going to go through anything, saying, 'Well, brother, as long as we're the salt, we're holding back the Antichrist.

00:09:32.030 --> 00:09:37.392
' I believe wholeheartedly that we are the salt and the restrainer because the Holy Ghost is in us.

00:09:40.055 --> 00:09:44.160
Some people believe we're going to go through the whole tribulation.

00:09:46.460 --> 00:09:46.695
I do not.

00:09:54.662 --> 00:09:56.451
I believe that we're not appointed unto wrath, and I believe with all my heart that we'll be taken out of here before all that mess starts.

00:09:56.451 --> 00:10:04.396
But it's not the beginning of sorrows, and I believe we're going to see some things before the Great Tribulation begins.

00:10:04.396 --> 00:10:06.760
That's just me.

00:10:08.470 --> 00:10:16.469
I believe some of the other people in my circle believe the same way.

00:10:20.530 --> 00:10:24.627
I'm telling you what I feel inside my spirit: the beginning, the birthing pains.

00:10:24.627 --> 00:10:32.400
As labor pains upon a woman, so will it be.

00:10:32.400 --> 00:10:39.815
I'm telling you, ladies and gentlemen, we're going to see some stuff.

00:10:39.815 --> 00:10:42.556
The Lord told me about what the word was, Braden.

00:10:42.556 --> 00:10:51.018
I want to say the exact word.

00:10:56.830 --> 00:10:57.000
He said, "I'm putting in my closers.

00:11:04.865 --> 00:11:05.170
" And closers are built for pressure.

00:11:16.566 --> 00:11:17.103
Great pressure is coming.

00:11:17.103 --> 00:11:20.980
You must have a sense of urgency.

00:11:20.980 --> 00:11:22.480
What's the C-word, Braden?

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:33.217
I've said it a thousand times today, and my mind, when I get on these live streams, just kind of goes.

00:11:33.217 --> 00:11:38.710
Obviously, we need to write this stuff down when He gives us these words because it's not our vocabulary.

00:11:38.710 --> 00:11:45.086
So, just knowing that we have to be that person with the backbone, with the crowbar.

00:11:45.086 --> 00:11:56.110
I'm trying to tell you all, the Lord's been talking to me outside while I've been cleaning and doing the things I've been doing.

00:11:56.110 --> 00:12:01.880
He said, "You must come at this stronger, for the great harvest of souls is ahead.

00:12:01.880 --> 00:12:11.627
For many are called, but few are chosen, for the harvest is plentiful and the labors are few.

00:12:22.440 --> 00:12:22.648
" That's why I'm having the urgency of saying, Braden, having the closer.

00:12:22.648 --> 00:12:33.813
Where we are right now in this dispensation, we're about to enter into the dispensation of judgment, but we're in grace for just this little bit of a window left.

00:12:33.813 --> 00:12:41.469
Right now, He's calling forth His church to have some urgency to bring in the harvest.

00:12:43.320 --> 00:13:02.425
That's why I was trying to tell you all yesterday, not that I was knocking having a hundred souls born again or having a few people getting born again, but I said, "Where is the church having major mass revival?

00:13:04.173 --> 00:13:07.670
" The Lord said to me, "Brandon, I'm waiting on the souls.

00:13:07.680 --> 00:13:12.020
I'm leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one.

00:13:12.020 --> 00:13:28.280
" That's why I was pushing in, saying, "Lord, anoint me with a special anointing, whatever it takes to bring in the harvest like a Billy Graham in these last days to bring in the lost.

00:13:28.280 --> 00:13:40.720
" If 170-some thousand people die daily and you only get a hundred people born again, I don't feel like that's great numbers.

00:13:40.720 --> 00:13:47.289
Even if we all got a hundred people saved, we need millions of people to get saved.

00:13:52.840 --> 00:13:52.973
I believe it's going to come through a great shaking to awaken.

00:13:52.973 --> 00:13:56.794
Every time I pray this, He says, "Brandon, that's why I'm bringing the shaking.

00:13:56.794 --> 00:14:01.260
Everything is going to be about a change within a 24-hour period.

00:14:01.260 --> 00:14:07.617
" He keeps talking about a major change within a 24-hour period.

00:14:07.617 --> 00:14:10.340
A major shaking is coming.

00:14:10.340 --> 00:14:15.520
Everything that we've ever known will change.

00:14:15.520 --> 00:14:24.669
When we went to the 23rd of September, He told me, "Brandon, after this timeframe, a great acceleration will come.

00:14:24.669 --> 00:14:30.400
A great acceleration will come from the 23rd of September, from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

00:14:30.400 --> 00:14:35.800
" He said, "Remember, as labor pains upon a woman, we see the acceleration and it's going.

00:14:35.800 --> 00:14:39.938
" He said, "This would be the time of the point of no return.

00:14:39.938 --> 00:14:41.694
It's time for the push.

00:14:41.694 --> 00:14:46.996
" When I say the point of no return, I'm talking about whenever a woman can get an epidural.

00:14:46.996 --> 00:14:52.760
There's only a certain time of the labor that you can get an epidural.

00:15:03.938 --> 00:15:04.267
But the Lord said to me, "Brandon, we are at that point right now of the push, as labor pains, to be contenders.

00:15:04.267 --> 00:15:05.911
" We must be contenders.

00:15:05.911 --> 00:15:09.860
We must fight for what's ours.

00:15:14.600 --> 00:15:14.800
You can't lay down and just feel sorry for yourself.

00:15:15.000 --> 00:15:17.748
The Lord said, "Brandon, I'm putting in the fighters.

00:15:17.748 --> 00:15:31.084
How bad do you want the outpouring of the Spirit of God on this last generation?

00:15:31.084 --> 00:15:40.806
" You think the devil's going to sit by and not try to put up a wall to restrain this or try to stop it?

00:15:40.806 --> 00:15:43.196
You're going to have to contend for it.

00:15:43.196 --> 00:15:56.480
You're going to have to have a bulldog-on-a-bone type of personality that says, "I'm the one that's going to make it upstream.

00:16:03.949 --> 00:16:04.091
I'm the salmon that's going to make it upstream.

00:16:04.091 --> 00:16:07.840
I'm going to be the one that witnesses into this earth.

00:16:07.840 --> 00:16:13.856
" That's why He said, "For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

00:16:13.856 --> 00:16:27.280
" As I observe church services and look at the pulse—and I'm not trying to pick at anybody, I'm telling you through the prophetic lens of what I'm praying over—where's the urgency in the church?

00:16:27.280 --> 00:16:31.380
People say, "Well, Brandon, you're too harsh.

00:16:31.380 --> 00:16:50.394
" As you drive down the road, the only way I can describe this to you is you can see the ones that are truly successful, the business owner versus the one that works for the one who owns the business.

00:16:59.194 --> 00:16:59.440
Your mentality has to change, thinking bigger for these end times.

00:16:59.440 --> 00:17:03.200
How big of a soul harvest are you believing for?

00:17:09.938 --> 00:17:10.373
If I just get one saved, folks, you've got to think bigger than that.

00:17:19.600 --> 00:17:19.747
The Lord said, "Brandon, believe bigger.

00:17:24.800 --> 00:17:25.605
I wish that none should perish, but all come to repentance.

00:17:25.605 --> 00:17:34.593
" What if we had all the people who've ever been saved for the last 2,000 years all saved within a couple of years?

00:17:34.593 --> 00:17:36.720
Greater works will you do.

00:17:45.480 --> 00:17:47.080
Think bigger.

00:17:47.080 --> 00:17:48.640
But what will it take?

00:17:48.640 --> 00:17:49.547
Money.

00:17:49.547 --> 00:17:51.360
It takes finances.

00:17:51.360 --> 00:18:01.380
How much money does it take to get the gospel out?

00:18:01.380 --> 00:18:03.537
Just for TV time, it takes millions of dollars.

00:18:03.537 --> 00:18:04.009
Believe big.

00:18:04.009 --> 00:18:07.183
He's exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:18:09.206 --> 00:18:11.125
And the Lord taught me it's time to expand your capacity.

00:18:11.330 --> 00:18:17.531
You need to think bigger for what I'm about to do in this end-time army.

00:18:17.531 --> 00:18:18.752
You're thinking too small.

00:18:18.752 --> 00:18:22.131
If I could believe God for a million dollars, that's a lot to me.

00:18:22.131 --> 00:18:25.720
But the Lord said, "You're thinking too small, Brandon.

00:18:30.937 --> 00:18:31.251
" I thought, "Wow.

00:18:41.760 --> 00:18:42.040
" For somebody who made minimum wage all their life, a million dollars will change your life.

00:18:42.040 --> 00:18:48.305
But to somebody who's already a multimillionaire, they look at it and say, "Braden, a million dollars ain't nothing.

00:18:48.305 --> 00:18:54.376
" But to somebody who hadn't had nothing, that's a lot.

00:19:04.340 --> 00:19:04.550
And the Lord said, "You need to think bigger.

00:19:04.550 --> 00:19:09.480
" That's why I drove through West Palm Beach.

00:19:09.480 --> 00:19:10.933
He said, "Look at Billionaire Road.

00:19:10.933 --> 00:19:12.857
Enlarge your capacity to believe Me.

00:19:12.857 --> 00:19:13.560
Think different.

00:19:13.560 --> 00:19:21.000
" So when I was looking at the souls, that's what I was trying to tell you all.

00:19:21.720 --> 00:19:35.960
When I was looking at the souls and things, you see Rodney Howard-Browne, he has big altar calls, and you see Billy Graham, but you don't see a lot of people having big altar calls anymore.

00:19:35.960 --> 00:19:49.132
Very seldom do you even see anybody—I go to a lot of churches and you don't see very many altar calls with even one or two people getting saved.

00:19:49.992 --> 00:19:50.336
I thought that's a shame.

00:19:50.336 --> 00:19:54.835
There has to be more.

00:19:54.835 --> 00:19:59.671
Because that's what He said when He's touching the doorknob.

00:20:00.142 --> 00:20:17.380
I looked at Him in the vision and I saw Jesus, and He said, "I'm waiting on My Father's instruction to tell Me to come and get you.

00:20:40.440 --> 00:20:40.714
" And I asked the Father, and it was thunderous.

00:20:40.714 --> 00:20:43.830
He said, "Brandon, you help Me bring in the harvest and I'll come and get you.

00:20:43.830 --> 00:20:46.740
That's all you're waiting on is a major outpouring.

00:20:46.740 --> 00:20:50.080
" So I thought, "What brings in the harvest?

00:20:50.080 --> 00:20:58.547
" My mind has just been turning because once you've experienced the glory one time—I'm not picking at anybody, but I'm looking for authentic.

00:20:58.547 --> 00:21:07.067
People say they've been to heaven, they've done this, they've done that.

00:21:07.067 --> 00:21:09.206
I'm looking for authentic.

00:21:14.525 --> 00:21:15.035
I want the presence when you're talking.

00:21:20.340 --> 00:21:35.227
If you say you've seen my Father, if you say you've seen my Jesus, is there a presence on you when you talk about it?

00:21:35.227 --> 00:21:42.749
Because when I'm telling you what I've been in front of, in his presence there's fullness of joy.

00:21:42.749 --> 00:21:46.430
In his presence, there's fullness of love.

00:22:06.080 --> 00:22:06.213
And I'm telling you, the glorious church will rise out of it.

00:22:06.213 --> 00:22:12.935
When you say you have an impartation from my Father, there should be fruit.

00:22:16.336 --> 00:22:17.408
I want to see fruit.

00:22:17.408 --> 00:22:23.445
I don't want to just hear words.

00:22:38.440 --> 00:22:38.813
I don't want to hear just a story.

00:22:41.768 --> 00:22:41.986
I want to see the glory.

00:22:41.986 --> 00:22:51.413
And I believe the people who walk with him are going to display glory.

00:22:51.413 --> 00:22:56.994
When you say that, I want to see glory on your face.

00:22:56.994 --> 00:23:02.480
I want to look upon his face.

00:23:03.240 --> 00:23:06.627
With one touch, with one breath, it'll change you forever.

00:23:06.627 --> 00:23:12.160
When you just behold his face, it will change you forever.

00:23:12.160 --> 00:23:14.240
You'll never be the same.

00:23:26.827 --> 00:23:27.260
A real radical touch from Jesus; you'll never be the same.

00:23:41.620 --> 00:23:41.835
It's that fire that never burns out; it's the water that never runs dry.

00:23:41.835 --> 00:23:43.373
Do you understand?

00:23:45.160 --> 00:24:06.500
And when you say you've seen him—whenever I've seen somebody who's authentically had an encounter with him, because I believe I have—it changes you.

00:24:10.124 --> 00:24:10.382
It makes you hungry.

00:24:16.640 --> 00:24:16.840
It makes you desperate.

00:24:16.840 --> 00:24:29.000
There's nothing more that you want other than just to get away from this world and go, 'How can I be with you?

00:24:29.000 --> 00:24:30.267
' There's nothing more.

00:24:36.284 --> 00:24:36.449
I don't care who you are.

00:24:36.449 --> 00:24:38.960
One touch, one drink, and you'll become addicted.

00:24:38.960 --> 00:24:44.320
Other than that, I question if you're authentic or not.

00:25:05.617 --> 00:25:06.069
I question you because I know when you touch it and you drink it, it changes you forever.

00:25:12.800 --> 00:25:13.730
And that's whenever he tells me, and I see it and I had these experiences with him.

00:25:15.480 --> 00:25:16.897
He says, 'Brandon, I'm coming.

00:25:16.897 --> 00:25:20.240
' And I'm like, 'There's nothing I want more.

00:25:32.110 --> 00:25:32.365
You couldn't offer me a fleet of Ferraris.

00:25:32.620 --> 00:25:35.640
You couldn't offer me a fleet of yachts.

00:25:35.640 --> 00:25:38.640
Jesus is all you want.

00:25:38.640 --> 00:25:53.910
Once you taste the glory, once you taste his presence, once you look upon his face, once you look into his eyes, there's nothing more you ever want.

00:25:53.910 --> 00:26:02.693
I remember he looked at me and he said, 'Brandon, are you willing to die for me?

00:26:02.693 --> 00:26:08.354
Are you willing to lay down your life for the cause if I ask you to?

00:26:08.354 --> 00:26:10.311
' Oh God, you ask so much.

00:26:11.385 --> 00:26:15.040
But yes, of course, whatever it takes to get this gospel out, Lord.

00:26:15.040 --> 00:26:47.204
Charlie Kirk, no matter how you get the threats, how many people try to come against you and tell you they want to hurt you, they want to do things to you, I have a family to protect, but at the same time, I know that all the disciples died other than one by martyrdom.

00:26:49.269 --> 00:26:52.464
What did it take to get the gospel out 2,000 years ago?

00:26:52.464 --> 00:26:53.543
What pressure?

00:26:53.543 --> 00:26:55.914
How much of a sacrifice?

00:26:55.914 --> 00:26:58.850
Why were they so radical?

00:26:58.850 --> 00:27:01.160
They had walked with him.

00:27:01.160 --> 00:27:04.211
They had been with him for three years.

