If I'm talking to you and you want to get born again tonight, you hear what I'm talking about, this urgency of where we are right now and you want Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior.

00:55:23.645 --> 00:55:23.970
I believe that today is your day for salvation.

00:55:35.755 --> 00:55:36.110
I believe that today is your day to turn your back on the world and Satan and all evil works and come to Jesus just as you are.

00:55:36.110 --> 00:55:38.712
'Oh, he'll never want me.

00:55:38.712 --> 00:55:40.780
No, no, no, no.

00:55:40.780 --> 00:55:43.390
' It doesn't matter what you've done.

00:55:43.390 --> 00:55:46.640
Jesus Christ paid the price for you to walk in victory over it.

00:55:46.640 --> 00:55:54.642
His blood washes all of it.

00:56:02.500 --> 00:56:13.324
The moment you confess your sins, he is faithful and just to forgive you of your sins and cleanse you of all unrighteousness.

00:56:13.324 --> 00:56:24.454
But you've got to confess it and you've got to get real with God.

00:56:34.354 --> 00:56:53.746
And the moment you get real with God, God will become real to you.

00:56:53.746 --> 00:56:57.500
Don't think religious, think relationship.

00:57:35.000 --> 00:57:35.187
I need you.

00:57:35.187 --> 00:57:42.400
So if that's you, I want you to put in the comment section down below, 'Tonight, I want to be saved.

00:57:42.400 --> 00:57:50.736
' Even if it's just one of you, I'm stretching the net out and I'm believing for a big harvest altogether.

00:57:50.736 --> 00:57:57.340
I'm looking for a lot of you to come to Jesus tonight.

00:58:01.369 --> 00:58:03.920
But I want you to put in the comment section right now, 'I want to be saved.

00:58:03.920 --> 00:58:14.440
' And if you're coming to Jesus, I want to say a simple prayer with you right now before we go to my intercessory prayer time.

00:58:14.440 --> 00:58:20.815
We'll see what the Lord has to show us about what's coming in the future.

00:58:39.440 --> 00:58:40.120
But I want you to give your heart to Jesus right now.

00:58:47.467 --> 00:58:47.920
Don't wait one more minute.

00:58:48.373 --> 00:58:49.280
Don't wait.

00:58:49.280 --> 00:58:58.750
So, I want to say a prayer with you.

00:58:58.750 --> 00:59:04.684
It's just a simple prayer.

00:59:04.684 --> 00:59:06.955
A five-year-old could say this.

00:59:06.955 --> 00:59:09.960
It doesn't have to be all religious.

00:59:09.960 --> 00:59:14.595
It's just something from the heart.

00:59:14.595 --> 00:59:22.293
Say, 'Jesus, I believe you're the son of God.

00:59:22.293 --> 00:59:33.911
I believe you died for me and you rose again on the third day.

00:59:33.911 --> 00:59:43.498
I believe you're seated at the right hand of the Father making intercession for me.

00:59:43.498 --> 00:59:55.840
Jesus, I'm a sinner and I ask you to forgive me of my sins.

00:59:55.840 --> 01:00:06.000
I ask you to wash me and cleanse me from all unrighteousness.

01:00:06.000 --> 01:00:19.510
Jesus, from this day forward, I turn my back on the world.

01:00:19.520 --> 01:00:27.926
I turn my back on the devil.

01:00:27.926 --> 01:00:32.900
I turn my back on my past.

01:00:38.160 --> 01:00:45.034
And from this day forward, Lord, I serve you with all my heart.

01:00:45.034 --> 01:00:49.840
Jesus, I thank you that you forgive me.

01:00:49.840 --> 01:01:01.067
Thank you, Lord, that you've washed me with your precious blood.

01:01:01.067 --> 01:01:13.246
Thank you, Lord, that my name is written in the Lamb's Book of Life.

01:01:13.246 --> 01:01:20.527
Write my name in there, Lord.

01:01:20.527 --> 01:01:25.550
Thank you, Jesus.

01:01:25.560 --> 01:01:30.720
I'll serve you forevermore.

01:01:45.280 --> 01:01:59.660
And if I mess up, Lord, I'll be quick to repent and keep running back to you.

01:02:14.560 --> 01:02:15.572
I love you, Jesus.

01:02:15.572 --> 01:02:23.062
And I thank you for what you did for me today.

01:02:23.062 --> 01:02:25.895
Amen and amen.

01:02:25.895 --> 01:02:29.866
' It's easy.

01:02:29.866 --> 01:02:49.920
Now, to be a Christian is not hard, but sometimes, you know, the pressures of life try to knock you down.

01:02:49.920 --> 01:03:05.937
But this is what happens when you fall down.

01:03:05.937 --> 01:03:15.680
You run to God when you sin.

01:03:15.680 --> 01:03:28.090
You don't run away from him.

01:04:24.787 --> 01:04:25.373
You run to him.

01:04:25.373 --> 01:04:30.994
Your sin is none of the devil's business anymore.

01:04:33.680 --> 01:04:36.371
You belong to Jesus and say, 'Jesus, I need your help.

01:04:36.371 --> 01:04:39.695
I can't do this on my own.

01:04:39.695 --> 01:04:42.640
I've fallen and I need help again.

01:04:42.640 --> 01:04:48.760
' So, you just keep going to the Father and you find scriptures.

01:04:48.760 --> 01:04:51.931
I want you to get a Bible.

01:04:51.931 --> 01:04:59.131
You read your Bible every day and you pray and you come here and pray with us.

01:04:59.131 --> 01:05:00.143
It's easy.

01:05:14.773 --> 01:05:15.307
You find a Bible-believing church, I'd say a non-denominational church.

01:05:15.307 --> 01:05:20.660
That's where I would go.

01:05:20.660 --> 01:05:22.410
Diana, my wife, would go.

01:05:25.343 --> 01:05:28.142
We go to a non-denominational church, and tell them, 'I need to be water-baptized.

01:05:28.142 --> 01:05:32.680
' Get water-baptized there and get plugged in there.

01:05:33.267 --> 01:05:46.227
Go on your Wednesdays and your Sundays or whatever kind of Bible study they may have, whatever.

01:05:46.227 --> 01:05:51.430
Get plugged in there.

01:05:51.440 --> 01:05:53.995
It might be a Thursday, Friday, Saturday, whatever.

01:05:53.995 --> 01:05:59.114
Go get plugged in.

01:05:59.114 --> 01:06:03.536
Get excited about this new life.

01:06:03.536 --> 01:06:06.407
You just accepted Jesus Christ.

01:06:06.407 --> 01:06:13.220
No, you need to understand what you did and become radically born again.

01:06:13.220 --> 01:06:14.448
Radical.

01:06:27.920 --> 01:06:28.171
And you may say, 'Brandon, I can't afford a Bible.

01:06:28.171 --> 01:06:29.889
I don't have a Bible.

01:06:29.889 --> 01:06:31.880
Could you help me get a Bible?

01:06:31.880 --> 01:06:41.303
' Well, my wife and I would want to celebrate your decision tonight of you giving your heart to Jesus Christ.

01:06:57.689 --> 01:06:57.947
And we will give you a Bible absolutely free.

01:06:57.947 --> 01:07:05.200
It'll be a New King James Version or King James or probably Amplified or something.

01:07:13.137 --> 01:07:13.509
I want you to tell us in the description down below.

01:07:13.509 --> 01:07:16.933
There's an email address down there.

01:07:18.053 --> 01:07:28.127
You email that email address and say in the headline, 'I got born again watching you and I would like to have my free Bible.

01:07:28.127 --> 01:07:50.286
' We'll send it to you from Amazon and you'll get it probably within a couple of days when Diana can get caught back up.

01:08:28.166 --> 01:08:28.613
We were gone to Branson at the prayer conference.

01:08:28.613 --> 01:08:34.540
So, we're a little behind, but I want to tell you, we will get it to you.

01:08:34.540 --> 01:08:43.394
But we want to celebrate your decision tonight to accept Jesus Christ as your Lord and personal Savior.

01:09:34.684 --> 01:09:34.907
And we just want to rejoice and be thankful.

01:09:34.907 --> 01:09:42.429
And so, God bless you and your decision that you made today.

01:09:42.429 --> 01:09:43.610
Well, how many?

01:09:43.610 --> 01:09:46.625
Did anybody get born again?

01:09:46.625 --> 01:09:47.595
73.

01:09:47.595 --> 01:09:50.053
73 salvations so far.

01:09:50.053 --> 01:09:51.405
That's wonderful.

01:09:55.885 --> 01:09:56.914
And so, I'm just believing God, you know, every single time we do this.

01:09:56.914 --> 01:10:01.000
100, but I'm believing for bigger.

01:10:01.000 --> 01:10:15.320
I'm believing for millions of people to understand where we are right now with the coming of the Lord Jesus Christ.

01:10:15.320 --> 01:10:23.284
He's coming and I don't want anybody to go to hell.

01:10:23.284 --> 01:10:29.670
Hell was not made for man; it was made for the devil and his demons.

01:10:44.110 --> 01:10:44.460
It wasn't made for us, but you choose to go there.

01:10:44.810 --> 01:10:50.800
And so many of you tonight, 70-some people accepted Jesus Christ.

01:10:50.800 --> 01:10:52.920
48 minutes.

01:10:52.920 --> 01:11:02.754
Thanks be—well, let's take communion and we'll pray for a little bit.

01:11:02.754 --> 01:11:04.240
All right.

01:11:04.240 --> 01:11:10.107
I hope every time we do these it stirs you.

01:11:10.107 --> 01:11:17.080
It causes urgency inside of you to know where we are right now.

01:11:19.390 --> 01:11:19.720
Be contenders.

01:11:19.720 --> 01:11:23.955
Thank you, Father, for your body that was broken for us.

01:11:37.540 --> 01:11:37.800
Thank you, Father, for this great nation.

01:11:37.800 --> 01:11:43.594
Thank you, Lord, that we're healed by your stripes.

01:11:56.720 --> 01:11:57.200
Lord, we take this body in the name of Jesus.

01:11:58.055 --> 01:12:05.507
And we're so grateful that you died for every single one of us.

01:12:05.507 --> 01:12:11.292
Father, what you bore in your body, we need not bear in our own.

01:12:11.292 --> 01:12:16.400
According to Galatians, Christ has redeemed us from the curse of the law.

01:12:20.520 --> 01:12:21.260
We have been redeemed from the curse.

01:12:21.260 --> 01:12:27.560
I am not under the curse; Jesus has set me free.

01:12:40.691 --> 01:12:41.126
For sickness, I have health; for poverty, wealth; for Christ has ransomed me.

01:12:41.126 --> 01:12:44.080
Do you believe that today?

01:12:44.080 --> 01:12:50.217
I am healed, whole, and well by the blood of my Jesus.

01:12:50.217 --> 01:12:53.840
Thank you, Lord, for taking it on your back.

01:12:53.840 --> 01:12:57.545
Thank you, Lord, that by your stripes I am healed.

01:12:57.545 --> 01:13:04.260
No sickness, no disease, no cancer, no diabetes, no heart disease, or whatever else is in this fallen world.

01:13:08.550 --> 01:13:15.017
Father, I believe that we are healed, whole, and well, and we are not under the curse of the law; Jesus has set us free.

01:13:17.640 --> 01:13:18.780
Thank you, Lord.

01:13:18.780 --> 01:13:22.000
Christ paid the price of the broken law.

01:13:22.000 --> 01:14:02.650
He paid the price for me and for you.

01:14:02.650 --> 01:14:03.950
Thank you, Father.

01:14:16.175 --> 01:14:16.410
I thank you, Lord, for the body that was broken for us.

01:14:44.640 --> 01:14:50.427
We take this body in the name of Jesus and we lift it up before you, Father.

01:14:51.013 --> 01:15:09.778
We give you all praise and glory for all that you have done for us.

01:15:41.766 --> 01:15:42.040
Father, I thank you, Lord, that we hear you, and a stranger's voice we will not follow, in Jesus' name.

01:15:42.040 --> 01:16:01.823
Now we take the blood, we apply the blood, and we make much of the blood, and the blood makes much of us.

01:16:01.823 --> 01:16:13.693
We confessed our sins tonight, Father, and we thank you, Lord, that you are faithful and just to forgive us of our sins and cleanse us from all unrighteousness.

01:16:13.693 --> 01:16:38.040
We apply the blood of Jesus over our households, over this room, over my wife and my children, over my finances, over my dog, and over the doorposts and windows of my house.

01:16:39.453 --> 01:16:41.097
The angels of the Lord are around us.

01:16:41.800 --> 01:16:46.430
The angels of the Lord ensure that no witchcraft, no incantation, no enchantment, nothing comes near us.

01:16:46.430 --> 01:16:50.926
Father, the blood covers us.

01:16:50.926 --> 01:16:53.540
I thank you, Lord, for the blood.

01:17:03.400 --> 01:17:03.640
The angels of the Lord are encamped around us, Father, and no weapon formed against us shall prosper.

01:17:17.617 --> 01:17:18.040
I thank you, Lord, that when we put our heads on the pillow, we sleep soundly, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

01:17:18.040 --> 01:17:22.063
Our life is dedicated and consecrated unto you.

01:17:36.360 --> 01:17:36.730
Father, we thank you for the blood that covers us.

01:17:36.730 --> 01:17:50.895
When we see, Father, we hear your voice and we won't be snared by any demonic spirits.

01:17:50.895 --> 01:17:54.960
We plead the blood over us, Father.

01:17:54.960 --> 01:18:06.655
When you show us things to come, we hear you and we apply the blood over our spiritual eyes.

01:18:06.655 --> 01:19:08.800
We apply the blood over us, Father, and we thank you, Lord.

01:19:08.800 --> 01:19:31.200
With great boldness, we decree and declare, for we believe that we arise and shine, for the light has come and the glory of the Lord is risen upon us tonight.

01:19:32.800 --> 01:19:35.320
And we take this blood in Jesus' name.

01:19:35.320 --> 01:19:36.056
Amen.

01:19:56.615 --> 01:20:00.047
You might say, 'Well, Brandon, that was different.

01:20:00.047 --> 01:20:07.370
' Well, yeah.

01:20:07.370 --> 01:20:10.448
I am not religious; I am about relationship.

01:20:10.448 --> 01:20:18.467
I told you, I don't do what traditional church does.

01:20:18.467 --> 01:20:22.462
I believe in having a relationship with Jesus Christ.

01:20:22.462 --> 01:20:26.747
All the other stuff is just bologna to me.

01:20:26.747 --> 01:20:30.928
I want to see fruit.

01:20:42.180 --> 01:20:42.480
The Bible says you will know them by their fruits.

01:20:42.480 --> 01:20:53.180
As my son, Brandon, said, people are always trying to change the fruit, but they have to change the root first.

01:21:06.430 --> 01:21:07.540
The fruit won't change until you change the root.

01:21:07.540 --> 01:21:13.067
Sometimes you have to do a root transplant.

01:21:13.067 --> 01:21:40.440
You have to pluck it out if it is not bearing fruit.

01:22:19.771 --> 01:22:20.337
It's like the fig tree that was not growing fruit; Jesus cursed it and it dried up from the root.

01:22:20.337 --> 01:22:28.440
If it isn't growing fruit, we need to pluck it up and plant something else.

01:22:28.440 --> 01:22:33.980
Believe God for a change in our lives.

01:22:33.980 --> 01:22:47.700
I am tired of being 'church normal'; I want to be 'church unusual.

01:22:47.700 --> 01:22:51.120
' I want to see the manifestation of the glory.

01:23:08.840 --> 01:23:15.539
I want to go to healing services, like when I go to see my friend Billy, and see the glory and people's lives radically changed.

01:23:15.539 --> 01:23:29.154
Father, we thank you, Lord.

01:23:29.154 --> 01:23:46.240
Open the eyes of my heart, Lord; I want to see you high and lifted up, shining in the light of your glory.

01:23:46.240 --> 01:23:55.280
Pour out your power and love as we sing, 'Holy, holy, holy.

01:23:55.280 --> 01:23:57.440
' Thank you, Lord, for your presence.

01:23:57.440 --> 01:24:07.600
Father, in your presence there is fullness of joy.

01:24:07.600 --> 01:24:13.950
In the presence of Jehovah, troubles vanish and hearts are mended.

01:24:13.950 --> 01:24:20.533
I may not know all the words every time, but I make a joyful noise unto the Lord.

01:24:20.533 --> 01:24:23.360
Everybody says, 'Well, you mess up on some words.

01:24:23.360 --> 01:24:29.580
' Yeah, I probably do, but I make a joyful noise unto the Lord.

01:24:29.580 --> 01:24:39.182
It's not for you; it's for him, because he inhabits my praises.

01:24:40.107 --> 01:24:41.262
That is what brings in the river.

01:24:41.262 --> 01:24:49.620
There is a river that flows, and I tap into it through worship.

01:25:01.231 --> 01:25:01.462
You don't come into the throne room rude; he is a king.

01:25:01.462 --> 01:25:09.972
Although I am able to go in boldly before the throne, I still go in with respect.

01:25:09.972 --> 01:25:13.272
Even as a child, I honor the position.

01:25:30.160 --> 01:25:30.316
I can go right up to him because he is my Father, but I honor him.

01:25:37.784 --> 01:25:38.136
He is worthy and holy, and he deserves reverence.

01:25:43.680 --> 01:25:46.051
We give you all the glory, praise, and honor.

01:25:57.943 --> 01:25:58.446
For the Lord, he is good and his mercy endures forever.

01:25:58.446 --> 01:26:02.135
You are great; you do miracles so great.

01:26:02.135 --> 01:26:07.507
There is no one else like you.

01:26:07.507 --> 01:26:10.135
You deserve the glory and the honor.

01:26:10.135 --> 01:26:20.010
Lord, we lift our hands in worship as we bless your holy name.

01:26:28.960 --> 01:26:29.902
I just love his presence.

01:26:29.902 --> 01:26:42.291
Brandon, this is the part I can spend time in.

01:26:42.291 --> 01:26:45.840
There is no one else like you.

01:26:45.840 --> 01:26:50.760
When praises go up, the blessings come down.

01:26:50.760 --> 01:27:02.149
For I believe in miracles; I have seen a soul set free.

01:27:02.149 --> 01:27:08.240
Miraculous, the changing one redeemed through Calvary.

01:27:16.020 --> 01:27:16.830
I have seen the lily push its way up through the stubborn sod.

01:27:39.840 --> 01:27:40.062
I believe in miracles, for I believe in God.

01:27:40.507 --> 01:27:44.223
I believe in miracles, for I believe in God.

01:27:44.223 --> 01:27:46.509
Thank You, Lord.

01:27:46.509 --> 01:27:51.143
Thank You, Lord, for we believe, Father, in miracles.

01:27:51.143 --> 01:28:10.560
We believe that there's nothing too big for You today, that there's an expiration date to every one of our problems.

01:28:10.560 --> 01:28:20.090
No matter how much we are going through in our day-to-day life, You have an expiration date for it.

01:28:20.090 --> 01:28:25.040
There is nothing too big for You, Jesus.

01:28:25.040 --> 01:28:34.032
If it's a hangnail or a cancer, nothing is too big.

01:28:34.032 --> 01:28:39.910
Nothing's too big, nothing's too small; Jesus paid the price for it all.

01:28:39.910 --> 01:28:47.977
We believe today that Jesus Christ is a healer.

01:28:47.977 --> 01:28:52.034
We believe today that Jesus Christ is a redeemer.

01:28:52.034 --> 01:28:56.857
We believe today that Jesus Christ is our deliverer.

01:28:56.857 --> 01:29:31.310
We have overcome him by the blood of the Lamb and the word of our testimony.

01:29:31.320 --> 01:29:33.940
Thank You, Father.

01:29:33.940 --> 01:29:36.560
Thank You, Father.

01:29:36.560 --> 01:29:45.000
Now, Lord, we enter in tonight and pray and go tubing.

01:29:45.000 --> 01:29:50.000
Who wants to go tubing?

01:30:29.760 --> 01:30:30.035
Say in the comment section.

01:30:33.440 --> 01:30:41.731
I always say as we go down the lazy river, you can go praying with me.

01:30:41.731 --> 01:30:46.640
Who wants to go tubing tonight?

01:30:46.640 --> 01:30:49.240
Let's go praying.

01:30:49.240 --> 01:30:51.480
How many are here right now?

01:30:51.480 --> 01:30:54.880
Okay, still the same.

01:30:54.880 --> 01:30:58.180
All right, ready?

01:30:58.180 --> 01:31:01.088
Oh, Father, we just worship You.

01:31:01.088 --> 01:31:03.240
You lead, we follow.

01:31:03.240 --> 01:31:07.100
We just lose sight of ourselves, Father.

01:31:07.100 --> 01:31:10.016
We just come before You boldly into Your throne room.

01:31:10.016 --> 01:31:22.427
We enter in by praise and thanksgiving, and we just love You.

01:31:22.427 --> 01:31:26.840
All the other stuff just melts off of us.

01:31:26.840 --> 01:31:37.929
Our cares take the care out of our prayer.

01:31:37.929 --> 01:31:41.776
Be careful for nothing; that's what the Bible says.

01:31:41.776 --> 01:31:47.951
We will not be careful about anything, but we take the care out of our prayer.

01:31:48.467 --> 01:32:23.332
And we thank You, Father, that tonight, no matter how much we see going on in this world, no matter how much we see going on in our households, or financially, or our marriages, or our children, or our unsaved loved ones, we know that just like You care for the sparrows of the air and the lilies of the field, Father, how much more do You care for us?

01:32:23.332 --> 01:32:25.040
You know all the needs.

01:32:25.040 --> 01:32:30.013
You know every hair on my head and the ones' lack thereof.

01:32:30.013 --> 01:32:31.720
You know how much I need.

01:32:31.720 --> 01:32:47.512
You know whatever I need; You said in Your word, Father, that You took care of it all way before I'd even asked for it.

01:32:47.512 --> 01:32:48.144
You knew it.

01:32:48.144 --> 01:32:50.886
You knew what I need.

01:32:58.070 --> 01:32:58.235
But Father, we just take our time and we just worship You tonight.

01:32:58.235 --> 01:33:04.640
And we're not worried about any of it.

01:33:20.217 --> 01:33:20.589
We have no anxiety about any of it because we're totally confident.

01:33:20.589 --> 01:33:27.080
We're fully persuaded that what God has promised, He's able also to perform.

01:33:27.080 --> 01:33:59.600
You have to understand that what God has promised—Abraham staggered not at the promise of God through unbelief, but he was fully persuaded that what God has promised, He's able also to perform.

01:33:59.600 --> 01:34:00.380
Fully persuaded.

01:34:06.120 --> 01:34:06.930
You can't talk him out of it, even in the deadness of Sarah's womb.

01:34:06.930 --> 01:34:34.166
So, Father, I thank You, Lord, that whatever we can help You with, whatever we need to pray, what's on Your heart, what's going on right now in the world—there's something we're going to stop or warnings of what's to come.

01:34:34.166 --> 01:34:36.824
Father, we yield.

01:34:36.824 --> 01:34:44.200
We thank You, Lord, that we hear You, Father, instantaneously.

